Enables access to objects across application domain boundaries in applications that support remoting.

Compare with System.ComponentModel.MarshallByValueComponent

PS C:\> (get-item .).getType().BaseType


----

See also the comment for Microsoft.Build.Utilities.AppDomainIsolatedTask:
  
    Provides the same functionality as Task, but also derives from
    MarshalByRefObject so that it can be instantiated in its own app domain.
